<html><head><title>Towers Perrin</title></head><body bgcolor="#ffffff"><img alt="Tower Perrin" width=500 height=55 src="towersperrin.gif"> <h4> At <b><i>Towers Perrin</i></b>, we view consulting as the art of building relationships to produce results.  Our relationships are based on trust and sustained by mutual respect and shared objectives.</h4><p align=center><a href="home.map"><img alt="Menu" border=0 width=295 height=240 src="home.gif" ismap></a></p><p align=center>| <b><i>Towers Perrin</i></b> <A HREF="preface.html">Preface</a> | <A HREF="headlines.html"><i>Headlines</i></i></A>| Worldwide <A HREF="offices.html">Offices</A> | <A HREF="mailto:ico@towers.com">ico@towers.com</A> | <a href="recruit.html">Recruitment</a> |
