<BODY>
 
<h2>CRISP's RESEARCH</H2>
<i>Last Modified : 19 December 1994</i>
<p><img src="pic/lookline.gif"><p>

<i>CRISP</i> intends to focus its research effort in the following areas:
<dl>
<dt><img src="pic/redball.gif"><b>  Technology</b>
<dl>
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Synthetic Aperture Radar Image Formation
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  SAR Interferometry
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  SAR Image Processing
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Digital Elevation Model Generation
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Fusion of Microwave and Optical Imagery
</dl>
<dt><img src="pic/redball.gif"><b>  Applications</b>
<dl>
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Cartography
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Environment Monitoring
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Forestry
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Ocean Phenomena
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Coastal Zone Monitoring
      <dt><img src="pic/orgball.gif">  Agriculture
</dl>
</dl>

<p><hr><p>
