<H3>TABLE 3.4    PLATFORM POSITION DATA RECORD</H3>
<P>
<P>

<PRE>
FIELD   BYTES   FORMAT  DESCRIPTION                                     CONTENT

1       1-4     B4      Record sequence number                          (4)
