                          &lt;AAAAAA-BB-CC-DD-EF> where:
                          AAAAAA = sensor identifier; BB = SAR band;
                          CC = resolution mode code;  DD = imaging mode code;
                          E  = transmit polarization; F  = receiver polarization
35     445-452    A8      Orbit number                                           &lt;......> 
