<head>
<title>VBJ Advertising Information</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
					VLINK="#E8171A"
					ALINK="#E8171A">

<body>


<center>
<img src="graphics/adinformation.gif" alt="The VBJ Advertising Information">
</center><br><br>


<b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b> accepts display and classified advertising in both the print and online editions. Special packages are available for advertisers who wish to take advantage of the opportunities created by using both mediums to communicate to The VBJ's readers.<p>

The VBJ in print is circulated throughout the world and has a readership of more than 20,000. The magazine is read by senior executives and key decision makers and is available by subscription and on newsstands worldwide. The VBJ can also be found at embassies, consulates and missions, as well as at most Vietnam-related associations and organizations.<p>

The VBJ has offices in both Hanoi and New York City. Additional advertising sales offices are located in Singapore, Thailand, Japan and Hong Kong.<p><br><br>

<center><font size=+2><b>Display and Classified Advertising Online</b></font></center><p>

Advertising on this site is available as a button, banner or classified listing. Buttons are found at the top of the "Homepage" and the "Current Issue" pages; banners are found at the top of the "Cover Story," "Company Profile," "FYI," "Street Talk," "Table of Contents" and "Editor's Letter" pages; and classified listing are found on the Classified Advertising page. For special opportunities for print advertisers, please send an e-mail to <a href="mailto:onlinead@viam.com">onlinead@viam.com</a>.<p>

<center>
<table border=1>
<caption><font color=3D6D92><b>1997 Online<br>Advertising Rates in US$</b></font></caption>
<tr><td width="125">Button<td width="100" align=right>$2,500/2 Months
<tr><td>Banner<td width="100" align=right>$1,000/2 Months
<tr><td>Button & Banner<td width="100" align=right>$3,000/2 Months
<tr><td>Classified Listing/50 Words<td width="100" align=right>$100/2 Months
</table>

<p><br><br>

<font color=3D6D92><b>Online Advertising Specifications</b></font></center><p>
<blockquote><blockquote>
1. Size and Format: A tile needs to be 150 x 60 pixels and a banner needs to be 420 x 100 pixels and should be in GIF or JPG format<p>
2. Links: All tiles and banners include a link to the advertiser's world wide web site or to a single page advertisement on The VBJ online. The single page must be under 80kb in total and is limited to 400 words of text and two graphics. Additional pages and/or content is available for a fee.<p>
3. Commitment: A minimum commitment of two months is required for all online advertising and links.<p>
4. Classifieds: Must be submitted as text. Links are permitted.<p>
5. Payment: Accounts must be paid in full within 10 days of invoice date. 2% discount for prepayment.<p>
6. Approved Advertising Agencies: Entitled to a 15% discount off published rates.</blockquote></blockquote><p><br><br>


