Classified advertising is accepted for the print edition of <b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b> for US$100.00 per column inch (a column is 2 5/16 inches or 59 mm). To place a classified advertisement, please send an e-mail to <a href="mailto:classifiedad@viam.com">classifiedad@viam.com</a>.<p><br><br>

