<head>
<title>VIAM Communications Group Ltd. Corporate Information</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"
					VLINK="#E8171A"
					ALINK="#E8171A">


<br><br><center>
<img src="graphics/viamlogo.gif" alt="VIAM Communications Group Ltd.">
</center>
<br><br>


<font size=+1><blockquote>
VIAM Communications Group Ltd. is a publishing company based in New York and Hanoi.  The company was formed in 1993 to publish information regarding Vietnam and South East Asia.  Print publications include <b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b> and the <b>V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> Y<small>ELLOW</small> P<small>AGES</small></b>.  The company also produces and sponsors conferences and seminars on Asian business issues as well as providing consulting services to companies seeking to do business in Vietnam.<p>

For more information about VIAM Communications Group Ltd. please write to VIAM's corporate relations department at 114 East 32nd Street, Suite 1010, New York, NY, 10016 or send an e-mail to <a href="mailto:corprelations@viam.com">corprelations@viam.com</a>.<p>




</blockquote></font><br clear>

<hr noshade width=85%><br>

<center>
<table border=0 width=95%>
<tr>
<td valign=top>
<td><a href="index.html"><img src="graphics/bannersm.gif" border=0 alt="The Vietnam Business Journal"></a>

<td>
<td><img src="graphics/v_break.gif"></td>
<td><td><td>

<td></b><p>
<b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b> delivers critical information and insightful analysis on doing business in Vietnam.  Written by journalists and industry experts based in Vietnam, and edited by professionals with years of Vietnam experience, <b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b> covers Asia's fastest-growing emerging market like no other publication.
Subscribers in more than 30 countries rely on <b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b> to provide practical information on doing business in Vietnam -- as well as how to make it a worthwhile investment of their time and money.<p>

Coverage of new business opportunities, the fast-changing legal system and the potential pitfalls of doing business in an emerging market are just some of the important issues featured regularly in <b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b>.<p>

To subscribe press <a href="subform.html">HERE</a>.

</table>
</center>
<br><br>

<hr noshade width=85%><br>


<center>
<table border=0 width=95%>
<tr>
<td valign=top>
<td><img src="graphics/yellowpages.gif" border=0 alt="The Vietnam Business Yellow Pages" align=right></a>

<td></td>
<td><img src="graphics/v_break.gif"></td>
<td><td><td>

<td><b>V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> Y<small>ELLOW</small> P<small>AGES</small></b>, published by VIAM Communications Group in late1994, includes over 20,000 company listings in 23 industry groups.  All information was prepared by the analysts and writers of <b>T<small>HE</small> V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> J<small>OURNAL</small></b>.<p>

The book also includes a colorful eight-page section on Vietnam providing important information on doing business in the country and on establishing relationships with Vietnamese partners.<p>

To order the <b>V<small>IETNAM</small> B<small>USINESS</small> Y<small>ELLOW</small> P<small>AGES</small></b>,<br>
send a check for $US50.00 plus shipping and handling<br>
(US$6.00 or US$20.00 outside the US) to<br>
VIAM Communications, 114 East 32nd Street,<br>
Suite 1010, New York, NY, 10016 USA.<br>
For faster delivery, e-mail or fax your Mastercard, Visa or<br>
American Express card number and<br>
expiration date to <a href="mailto:yellowpages@viam.com">yellowpages@viam.com</a> or 212-727-8160.

</table>
